Summary: ufo in eastern sky, cylindrical w/ black line in middle
trends: There have been 4 other sightings in Spring Hill
There were no other sightings in Spring Hill on or around June 14th 2005
divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my pool swimming, with my brother. My bro told me to look, so I did and saw a cylindrical object with a black line in middle. when i first glimpsed at it i thought it was an airplane, but then i saw the shape of it. It was cylindrical with a black line in the middle. it went north in the east sky. I was amazed and i just kept looking at it. I lost it when it went behind a tree and it never came back in sight
